{"title":"大山情怀","authors":["佟石"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":9,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大山情怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佟石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每颗山民的心都长满情节一代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是一章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有个病弱者来读了一遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便获得了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山峰的骨骼山泉的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一次挂绿又一次披红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如年轻的女郎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临风舞蹈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说她已几百岁几千岁了呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她却微微一笑——大山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不相信年龄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你恨那昏黑的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便伸出银臂把山峰推醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但当群山举起戳天的剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你却成了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天的护心镜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山民与故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是山民养育了故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是故事养育了山民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当多少人与旧的故事告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转过身来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又成了新故事的主人公"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}